  <item nodeId="node-1108">
    <command xml:space="preserve">1</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">[Share your speculation.]&#x000A;&#x000A;"I will not know what it is I'm saying, but I have a guess about what will happen.&#x000A;&#x000A;And no capsae holder I have yet met will risk such a thing," you say.&#x000A;&#x000A;1) {Switching to Constance}: Scoff at "capsae holder".&#x000A;2) {Switching to Constance}: Ask about his guess.&#x000A;3) OK, I'm a tester and I need to skip ahead and be Constance, fiddling with scrolls and stuff.&#x000A;4) I'm also a tester, and I just want to go back to the beginning of this conversation.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
