    <command xml:space="preserve">open black</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">(the black capsa)&#x000A;You open the black capsa, revealing a scroll of igram.&#x000A;&#x000A;For a moment, the purple capsa seems to flicker.  But you look again, and nothing seems to have changed.&#x000A;The hunting cloaks disappear again.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
